cannot be replicated
when you let it grow

172
00:09:42,748 --> 00:09:45,384
into thousands and thousands
of people at the same time.

173
00:09:45,384 --> 00:09:47,954
So I wish you the very
best in this conference.

174
00:09:47,954 --> 00:09:50,623
I am honored to be here to
welcome you to it

175
00:09:50,623 --> 00:09:54,026
and I wish you the richest of ca-discussions

176
00:09:54,026 --> 00:09:58,431
and, and, um, new discoveries being discussed here.

177
00:09:58,431 --> 00:10:00,566
Thank you very
much for having me.

