260
00:14:46,852 --> 00:14:48,854
and he has received many honors,

261
00:14:48,854 --> 00:14:52,224
among them
six honorary doctorates,

262
00:14:52,224 --> 00:14:57,329
eh, the 1985 Oldenburger Medal from the, eh,

