280
00:16:11,403 --> 00:16:14,306
I should also tell the students,
sitting there in the back,

281
00:16:14,306 --> 00:16:15,974
there are a couple
of seats up front.

282
00:16:15,974 --> 00:16:19,244
Don't be shy, but step forward
