00:26:15,173 --> 00:26:17,208
[laughing]

510
00:26:17,208 --> 00:26:18,977
The other thing about feedback

511
00:26:18,977 --> 00:26:21,746
is that you are feeding sensor noise into the system

512
00:26:21,746 --> 00:26:24,582
so that noise will create
a lot of action

513
00:26:24,582 --> 00:26:25,717
that you would like to avoid.

