00:26:25,717 --> 00:26:27,152
So these are the two drawbacks.

515
00:26:27,152 --> 00:26:29,621
But, of course, if you look
to the advantages

516
00:26:29,621 --> 00:26:31,656
we have a lot of positive things going for us.

517
00:26:32,824 --> 00:26:35,427
So the scene of 1940 was
widespread use of control

