00:26:59,951 --> 00:27:03,722
want organized laboratories around universities

529
00:27:03,722 --> 00:27:06,891
which were going to develop the m-m-military tools,

530
00:27:06,891 --> 00:27:07,892
the radar, etc.

531
00:27:07,892 --> 00:27:10,528
And of course very prominent here in the United States

532
00:27:10,528 --> 00:27:12,597
was the effort around MIT.

533
00:27:12,597 --> 00:27:14,833
So I want to, gunsights,
radar, etc.

534
00:27:14,833 --> 00:27:17,102
So the concepts were to use feedback and feedforward.

535
00:27:17,102 --> 00:27:19,204
And what happened then is that
they brought in people

536
00:27:19,204 --> 00:27:20,872
who had very different talents.

537
00:27:20,872 --> 00:27:22,307
They brought in people,
for example,

538
00:27:22,307 --> 00:27:24,042
who new about autopilots.

