00:27:24,042 --> 00:27:26,044
They brought in
people from Bell Labs.

540
00:27:26,044 --> 00:27:28,413
They brought in people from
the process control industry.

541
00:27:28,413 --> 00:27:29,714
And then people discovered

542
00:27:29,714 --> 00:27:31,716
we have actually been doing
the same thing.

