00:27:48,867 --> 00:27:50,869
And at that time
there was a holistic view

551
00:27:50,869 --> 00:27:52,070
of theory and applications.

552
00:27:52,070 --> 00:27:55,073
So, essentially, the same groups
who were doing application,

