00:28:44,122 --> 00:28:48,059
and a first rate abstract mathematician, Ralph Phillips

574
00:28:48,059 --> 00:28:50,295
from, eh, University
of Southern California.

575
00:28:50,295 --> 00:28:53,832
Cert its conception,
control was multidisciplinary

576
00:28:53,832 --> 00:28:55,834
with a strong footing
in mathematics,

577
00:28:55,834 --> 00:28:57,135
a strong footing in physics,

578
00:28:57,135 --> 00:28:59,003
and a strong footing
in instrumentation.

579
00:29:01,005 --> 00:29:03,608
The consequences
of this were tremendous.

580
00:29:03,608 --> 00:29:06,878
We were getting e-education of
control engineers, sort of.

581
00:29:06,878 --> 00:29:08,913
Control courses
sprung up everywhere.

582
00:29:08,913 --> 00:29:10,915
They came in different
departments, mechanical,

