00:29:10,915 --> 00:29:13,651
electric, sometimes
in civil engineering.

584
00:29:13,651 --> 00:29:16,721
Eh, we got organizations where
the most prominent is IFAC,

585
00:29:16,721 --> 00:29:18,723
International Federation
of Automatic Control,

