00:34:41,979 --> 00:34:44,315
and it's trying to estimate
what the wave motion is.

719
00:34:44,315 --> 00:34:45,316
And you can also see,

720
00:34:45,316 --> 00:34:48,119
we are not using
larger rudder motions

721
00:34:48,119 --> 00:34:50,121
than what you are doing
with the PID controller.

722
00:34:50,121 --> 00:34:52,123
That's a little bit more
high frequency in here.

723
00:34:52,123 --> 00:34:54,292
So I would say that this is a
very nice example of

724
00:34:54,292 --> 00:34:55,893
adaptive control

725
00:34:55,893 --> 00:34:58,729
that was done 30 years ago,

726
00:34:58,729 --> 00:35:01,799
and the products are still here, here running.

727
00:35:01,799 --> 00:35:05,570
One nice thing here is that you
