00:35:09,040 --> 00:35:11,042
So if you know basic data
about the ship,

731
00:35:11,042 --> 00:35:12,176
you can roughly figure out

732
00:35:12,176 --> 00:35:13,778
what the initial parameters
are going to be.

733
00:35:16,247 --> 00:35:19,550
Em, here's a special
subject I will take up.

734
00:35:19,550 --> 00:35:23,688
Because in the early phase
