744
00:35:49,580 --> 00:35:52,083
So then people say,
eh, well, y'know,

745
00:35:52,083 --> 00:35:55,353
maybe these limitations
are not so serious anyway.

746
00:35:55,353 --> 00:35:57,355
And, eh, uh,
I attended conference

747
00:35:57,355 --> 00:35:58,556
that were violent discussions,

748
00:35:58,556 --> 00:36:00,992
y'know, between the people
who were advocating,

749
00:36:00,992 --> 00:36:03,294
what was at the time called, modern control theory

750
00:36:03,294 --> 00:36:04,929
and the classic guys.

751
00:36:04,929 --> 00:36:06,931
The classic guys were saying
like this,

752
00:36:06,931 --> 00:36:10,668
oh, time delays are limitations.

753
00:36:10,668 --> 00:36:13,137
It must come into the theory.

754
00:36:13,137 --> 00:36:15,139
Zeros in the right-half-planes
are very bad.

755
00:36:15,139 --> 00:36:16,207
They must come in.

756
00:36:16,207 --> 00:36:19,176
And then the guys sitting there
