1360
01:00:40,937 --> 01:00:42,372
y'know, forget about the rest.

1361
01:00:42,372 --> 01:00:44,774
Dive into it an-and develop
the mathematics.

1362
01:00:44,774 --> 01:00:46,876
And we still have to do this
