1363
01:00:46,876 --> 01:00:49,612
but to serve the engineering world that's sitting out there,

1364
01:00:49,612 --> 01:00:52,715
we must also have people who have a holistic view of things

1365
01:00:52,715 --> 01:00:54,083
and that's a major challenge

1366
01:00:54,083 --> 01:00:56,419
